{
  "stem": "2684.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he could get tickets because the trials and the hanging was public.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And it happened in the Zeneakademia, which is conservatorium in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And that's where trials took place in front of a people judge, with galleries full of people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But you need a ticket to get there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And when I came home from concentration camps, my father wanted me to go.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And he thought that my conscious would ease if these people come to justice.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From then on, from Kosice to Auschwitz, I cannot remember whether the door had been opened or not, or whether we got water or not.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because the whole trip took, Thursday we left, Friday, Saturday, Sunday we arrived to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So approximately 2 and 1/2 days we were on the train.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And during that time, people died in the wagon.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we couldn't get rid of them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had to-- they had to stay.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The wagon was so packed that, if I was on one side of the wagon, which is not long-- it was about 10 meters, 11 meters.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I didn't know what's happening in the other end of the wagon.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because, between me and the end of the wagon, another, I don't know how many, hundreds of people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We were actually like sardines.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The door was locked.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Scream was heard.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We heard people talking absolutely out of ordinary, which mean we knew that they became mad on the trip.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And what I remember after that is, when they opened the wagon, and we came out to the platform, and it was a lot of people.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It's a lot of people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was like a tidal wave.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we didn't know where we were.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I never forget-- the train stops.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
